sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Siswa
    participant View as Peta Level (Blade)
    participant Ctrl as MisiController
    participant DB as Database & Models

    rect rgb(30, 41, 59)
    note right of Siswa: FASE 1: CEK KUOTA TIKET (SERVER)
    Siswa->>View: Membuka Peta Level
    View->>Ctrl: GET showLevels()
    Ctrl->>DB: Cek used_count tiket hari ini
    DB-->>Ctrl: Data tiket ditemukan
    Ctrl-->>View: Tampilkan sisa tiket (3 - used_count)
    end

    rect rgb(15, 23, 42)
    note right of Siswa: FASE 2: TRANSAKSI PENUKARAN (ACTION)
    Siswa->>View: Klik "Tukar Tiket" pada misi
    View->>Ctrl: POST /misi/retry/{id}
    
    note over Ctrl,DB: Validasi Kuota (If/Else)
    alt [used_count < 3]
        Ctrl->>DB: Reset Attempts = 0 & Status = In Progress
        Ctrl->>DB: Tiket used_count + 1
        Ctrl-->>View: Redirect ke Halaman Misi
        View-->>Siswa: Misi terbuka (Potensi Skor Maksimal)
    else [used_count >= 3]
        Ctrl-->>View: Redirect Back (Error)
        View-->>Siswa: Alert "Jatah Tiket Habis"
    end
    end